Derrough Says Financing of M&A Market `Choppy'

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-27T22:21:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/derrough-says-financing-of-m-a-market-choppy-video.html
William Derrough, managing director
at Moelis & Co., Debra Cafaro, chief executive officer of Ventas
Inc., and Frederick Frank, vice chairman of Peter J. Solomon 
Co., speak about the merger and acquisition market, and the 
outlook for private equity, leveraged loans and real estate 
deals.  They speak with Pimm Fox on Bloomberg Television's "Taking 
Stock." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 11:52
 